# Per-worktree dev slots (#194). The manifest is host-local — slot
# numbers describe a single VM's port layout and shouldn't propagate
# across machines. The worktrees/ directory holds linked git worktrees
# created by `just worktree-new` and is similarly local.
/.dev-slots.json
/worktrees/
**/.env.slot
